HEADWORD: Lustre
<hw>Lus"tre</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Same as
<er>Luster</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lustrical</ent>⟦br⟧
